{"tid":1440167,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[恐嚇?]福建社團聯會籲福建鄉親周日勿外出","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T11:29:03.000Z","uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"268cee5e3ab0d10c8dd89f7d765c9beb11ae2f3c","tid":1440167,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】福建社團聯會舉行反暴力誓師大會，聯會榮譽顧問盧文端呼籲福建鄉親周日不要外出，又指「人若犯我，我必自衛」，聯會主席吳換炎強調福建幫不會打人。<br />\n<br />\n誓師大會有逾百人出席，指對香港目前的暴力和混亂表示極度不滿和反感，要求「止暴制亂」社會恢復秩序，並會化為一項項的行動，表明「人若犯我，我必自衛」。<br />\n<br />\n福建社團聯會榮譽顧問盧文端呼籲福建鄉親周日不要外出。聯會主席吳換炎解釋呼籲不要外出，是避免發生衝突，強調福建幫不會打人。<br />\n<br />\n誓師大會上未有交代所謂「自衛」的具體行動，吳換炎只說若有人侵犯他們會報警求助，強調自衛是靠警方守住會所，不會外出自衛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358667&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358667%26refer%3D&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPPZItop%2BIuorIKtd308SUMA%3D&h=9d43ff88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358667%26refer%3D&h=e31a1e50\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=358667&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"ded437cd1cdc7689b274d58373073c9296950c99","tid":1440167,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391a89a8294104e2b2cd832a2de7ce9a060ac9e4","tid":1440167,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}